<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Layer-Cache on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/layer-cache/</link><description>Recent content in Layer-Cache on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/layer-cache/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Docker Cache Not Found — cache not found</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/docker/layer-cache/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/docker/layer-cache/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="docker-cache-not-found--cache-not-found-in-scope"&gt;Docker Cache Not Found — cache not found in scope&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Docker cannot find a cached layer for a build step. It forces a rebuild of all subsequent layers, slowing down the build process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous build layer changed, invalidating cache&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dockerfile instructions reordered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build arguments changed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;.dockerignore&lt;/code&gt; excludes cached files&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="order-dockerfile-instructions-by-change-frequency"&gt;Order Dockerfile Instructions by Change Frequency&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dockerfile" data-lang="dockerfile"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Install dependencies first (rarely changes)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; package*.json ./&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; npm install&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Then copy source code (changes often)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; . .&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-buildkit-cache-mounts"&gt;Use BuildKit Cache Mounts&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dockerfile" data-lang="dockerfile"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# syntax=docker/dockerfile:1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; --mount&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;type&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;cache,target&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/root/.cache/npm npm install&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-docker-build-cache-from-registry"&gt;Use Docker Build Cache from Registry&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker build --cache-from registry/image:tag -t image:tag .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="disable-cache-for-debugging"&gt;Disable Cache (for debugging)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker build --no-cache -t &amp;lt;image&amp;gt; .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="multi-stage-build-with-cache"&gt;Multi-Stage Build with Cache&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dockerfile" data-lang="dockerfile"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;node:18&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AS&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;deps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WORKDIR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;/app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; package*.json ./&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; npm ci --only&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;production&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;node:18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WORKDIR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;/app&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; --from&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;deps /app/node_modules ./node_modules&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;COPY&lt;/span&gt; . .&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 1: Check if cache is being used&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker build -t myapp .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Step 3/5 : COPY package*.json ./&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# ---&amp;gt; Using cache&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 2: Force rebuild without cache&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker build --no-cache -t myapp .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 3: Use BuildKit for better caching&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;DOCKER_BUILDKIT&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; docker build -t myapp .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/docker/build-failed2/"&gt;Build Failed&lt;/a&gt; — COPY failed during build&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/docker/no-space/"&gt;No Space Left&lt;/a&gt; — disk space exhausted&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>